{"tid":1117570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"搵老公一定要搵好似馬明咁","createTime":"2019-04-20T18:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T02:34:08.000Z","uid":136933,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea491e79c8f3ba40722e0b661ff357746f6d706f","tid":1117570,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗解釋<br />\n孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個年代好少人會拖住呀媽出街 仲要好為屋企人著想<br />\n毒毒地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有晒安全感 又夠可愛<br />\n唔煙唔酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酒都唔掂好難得<br />\n<br />\n想像下下半世同馬明咁既男人過<br />\n諗到都濕濕地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2200f3434dbd910b9dc36fa5321279cf79b2c622","tid":1117570,"uid":225760,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:19:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1abf0fa004f3e900661bfc4caa1767b16a885bc","tid":1117570,"uid":136933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2200f3434dbd910b9dc36fa5321279cf79b2c622","tid":1117570,"uid":225760,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:19:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:21:54.000Z","msg":"唔係個個女人都好似賓穎隻死臭雞咁<br />\n馬明係我既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會好好珍惜佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88ca9b56420532027efb8a9158faab583a7f75f","tid":1117570,"uid":136933,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馬明你見到呢個post既話<br />\n你要知道<br />\n香港仲有好多女仔排緊隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lov